review_data: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2021
name: Online Shopper, United States
title: Too many carbs!
review: Too many carbs!It's okay if you don't finish all the honey.This serving size has a ridiculous amount of empty sugar carbohydrates.The other (fruit) flavors of this split cup 2% Fage have much lower carbs.There's 2 - 3 times as much honey in this one as you need for the amount of yogurt.It's good honey, though, with a nice, floral scent.

name: Karen D Garman
title: Don’t waste plastic and honey get a larger container and buy honey to add to it.
review: So I really liked the yogurt and the honey but I was amazed at how much honey is included. There’s no way anyone could eat that much honey with that much yogurt. I don’t like to buy products that make me feel like a glutton and a wasteful Amercican. Next time I will be a large container of this yogurt and some honey separate and mix them myself.

title: So good.
review: God, I love this so much. The slight tart of the plain greek yogurt with the sweet and delicious honey is the perfect contrast. I recommend not stirring it like crazy and mixing it. Just push the honey into the yogurt a few times or leave it layered on top. So good.
